{"id":1352,"date":"2021-07-21T14:25:03","date_gmt":"2021-07-21T14:25:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/?page_id=1352"},"modified":"2022-10-22T21:49:41","modified_gmt":"2022-10-22T21:49:41","slug":"bariatric-surgery","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/bariatric-surgery\/","title":{"rendered":"Bariatric Surgery"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"1352\" class=\"elementor elementor-1352\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-section-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-237806f elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"237806f\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-24d83c2\" data-id=\"24d83c2\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8178bf5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8178bf5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h1 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Stomach: Bariatric Surgery<\/h1>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3fb9b3c elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3fb9b3c\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cc88e83\" data-id=\"cc88e83\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8fa06ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8fa06ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Laparoscopic Adjustable Gastric Banding (LAGB)<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-95211b8 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"95211b8\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-05b26fe\" data-id=\"05b26fe\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-990daa1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"990daa1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Procedure<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Expose Left Crus at the Angle of His<\/li><li>Dissect the Gastrohepatic Ligament to Enter the Lesser Sac<\/li><li>Place Band Around Proximal Stomach<ul><li>Medial-to-Lateral Direction (45-Degree Angle to Left Shoulder)<\/li><li>Inferior-to-Superior Slant<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Pull Tubing Externally &amp; Secure to the Subcutaneous Port<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Complications<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Band Slippage<\/em><ul><li>Herniation of Stomach Above the Band<\/li><li>UGI: Fundus Above Band<ul><li>Band on XR Should Be at 45-Degree Angle (90-Degree or More is Indicative of Slippage)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Tx: <strong>Deflate Band<\/strong> (Remove Saline) &amp; <strong>Surgically Remove<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Gastric Erosion<\/em><ul><li>Erosion of the Band into the Stomach<\/li><li>Presentation:<strong> Erythema<\/strong> &amp; <strong>Tenderness<\/strong> at Port Site<\/li><li>UGI: Contrast Outside of Lumen<\/li><li>Tx: Remove Band &amp; Repair Defect<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Tube Kinking<\/em><ul><li>Presentation: Difficulty Adding\/Removing Fluid from Port<\/li><li>Tx: <strong>Explore Under Local Anesthesia<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Band Too Tight<\/em><ul><li>UGI: Esophageal Dilation<\/li><li>Tx: <strong>Deflate Band<\/strong> or <strong>Surgically Remove<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Vertical Banded Gastroplasty (VBG)<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>A Vertical Staple Line Through the Proximal Stomach with a Band Placed Around the Middle of the Stomach at the End of the Staple-Line to Create a Small Pouch<\/li><li>Fallen Out of Favor<\/li><li>Only 10% Maintain Weight Loss After 10 Years<ul><li>Restrictive Nature Causes Difficulty Tolerating High Fiber\/Protein Diet<\/li><li>Many Result to Liquid Carbs and Junk Food Causing Weight Regain<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-1f15990\" data-id=\"1f15990\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b7d6c06 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b7d6c06\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-10685 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Gastric-Band.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"674\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Gastric-Band.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Gastric-Band-223x300.jpg 223w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>LAGB <sup>1<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7d45716 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7d45716\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-10682 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Vertical-Banded-Gastroplasty.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"631\" height=\"597\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Vertical-Banded-Gastroplasty.jpg 631w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Vertical-Banded-Gastroplasty-300x284.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 631px) 100vw, 631px\" \/><\/p><p>VBG <sup>2<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ebe662d elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"ebe662d\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-01a427b\" data-id=\"01a427b\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a671c94 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a671c94\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Laparoscopic Vertical Sleeve Gastrectomy (LVSG)<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-4eb8869 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"4eb8869\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-5c82635\" data-id=\"5c82635\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ffb67fd elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ffb67fd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Procedure<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Divide the Short Gastric Vessels Along the Greater Curvature<\/li><li>Pass Bougie Orally and Direct Along the Lesser Curvature<\/li><li>Divide Stomach Along the Greater Curvature<ul><li>Start <strong>5-6 cm from Pylorus<\/strong> (Obstructs if Too Close)<\/li><li>Extend to Angle of His<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-e00a548\" data-id=\"e00a548\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-380d4a4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"380d4a4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-10686 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Sleeve-Gastrectomy.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"803\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Sleeve-Gastrectomy.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Sleeve-Gastrectomy-187x300.jpg 187w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>LVSG <sup>1<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-5fb86c4 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"5fb86c4\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-fcbf15c\" data-id=\"fcbf15c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-825fe9f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"825fe9f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Roux-en-Y Gastric Bypass (RYGB)<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2a0f035 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"2a0f035\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-68c56bd\" data-id=\"68c56bd\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ce2d351 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ce2d351\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Procedure<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Divide Jejunum 30-50 cm (Biliopancreatic Limb) Distal to Ligament of Treitz<\/li><li>Anastomose Proximal End 75-150 cm (Roux Limb) Down Distal Jejunum<\/li><li>Expose Left Crus at the Angle of His<\/li><li>Dissect the Gastrohepatic Ligament to Enter the Lesser Sac<\/li><li>Transect Stomach to Create a 20 cc Proximal Gastric Pouch<\/li><li>Anastomose Roux Limb to Gastric Pouch<\/li><li>Close Mesenteric Defects<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Mesenteric Defects<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Jenjuno-Jejunostomy Defect<\/em><\/li><li><em>Petersen\u2019s Space<\/em><ul><li>Between Roux Limb Mesentery &amp; Transverse Mesocolon<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Transverse Mesocolon Defect<\/em><ul><li>Only Present After Retrocolic Procedures<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Roux Limb Variations<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Antecolic<\/em> \u2013 Roux Limb Passed Anterior to Transverse Colon<ul><li>Faster to Preform<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Retrocolic<\/em> \u2013 Roux Limb Passed Posterior to Transverse Colon<ul><li>Shorter Route (Less Ischemia Risk)<\/li><li>Higher Risk for Internal Hernia<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Complications<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Failure &amp; Weight Regain<\/em> (15%, Long Term 35%)<ul><li>Definition: BMI &gt; 35 or Failure to Achieve\/Maintain \u2265 50% of Excess Weight Loss<\/li><li>Most Often Due to Maladaptive &amp; Noncompliant Eating Habits<ul><li>Pouch Can Stretch\/Dilate from Repeated Overdistention<\/li><li>Unlikely to Benefit from Revisional Surgery<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Can Be Caused by a Gastrogastric Fistula<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Anastomotic Leak<\/em> (0-5%)<ul><li>Consider Barium Swallow on Postoperative Day #2<\/li><li>Most Common Cause: Ischemia<\/li><li>Sx: <strong>Tachycardia (First)<\/strong>, Tachypnea, Fever &amp; Often Have No Pain<ul><li>Any Evidence of New Onset Tachycardia Could Suggest a Leak<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Tx:<ul><li>Unstable or Early (Not Contained): Surgery<\/li><li>Stable &amp; Late (Contained): IR Drain &amp; ABX<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Stomal\/Anastomotic Stenosis<\/em> (6-17%)<ul><li>Manifests When Anastomosis Diameter Narrow &lt; 10 mm<\/li><li>Presentation: Unable to Swallow Liquids<\/li><li>Tx: Endoscopic Dilation<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Marginal Ulcers<\/em> (0.6-16%)<ul><li><strong>Advise All Patient to Avoid Smoking &amp; NSAIDs<\/strong><\/li><li><a href=\"http:\/\/operativereview.com\/gastrectomy\">*See Stomach: Gastrectomy<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Gastrogastric Fistula<\/em> (1-2%)<ul><li>Fistula Between Stomach Pouch &amp; Stomach Remnant<\/li><li>Presentation: Marginal Ulcers, Pain, Bleeding or Weight Gain<\/li><li>Tx: Endoscopy vs Surgery<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Internal Hernia<\/em> (3-5%)<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/internal-hernia\/\">*See Small Intestine: Internal Hernia<\/a><\/li><li><strong>Most Common Cause of SBO<\/strong> after RNY (Not Adhesions)<\/li><li>Herniated Bowel Through Internal Mesenteric Defect<\/li><li>See Mesenteric Swirl on CT<\/li><li>Cause: Poor Closure of Defects<ul><li>Increased Risk in Laparoscopic Surgery (Less Adhesions &gt; More Mobility)<\/li><li>Most Common Defect: Transverse Mesocolon (Less With Antecolic Limb)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Tx: <strong>Surgery<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Gallstones<\/em><ul><li>Cause: Stasis &amp; Increased Calcium\/Mucin Secretion<ul><li>Rapid Weight Loss Increases Lithogenicity of Bile<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Asymptomatic Gallstones are Common but <strong>Symptoms are Rare<\/strong><\/li><li>Difficult to Preform ERCP for Choledocholithiasis After RYGB Due to Altered Anatomy<ul><li>May Require Surgical Gastrostomy into Remnant to Pass the Endoscope<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Some Recommend Prophylactic Cholecystectomy at Time of Original Surgery (Controversial)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Dumping Syndrome<\/em><ul><li><a href=\"http:\/\/operativereview.com\/gastric-emptying-diseases\">*See Stomach: Gastric Emptying Diseases<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Candy Cane Roux Syndrome<\/em><ul><li>Excessively Long Blind Afferent Roux Limb at the Gastrojejunostomy<\/li><li>Presentation: Postprandial Pain Relieved by Vomiting<\/li><li>Dx: UGI or Endoscopy<\/li><li>Tx: Surgical Revision<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Gastric Remnant Distention<\/em><ul><li>Risk for Rupture<\/li><li>Tx: Emergent Gastrostomy Tube for Decompression<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>B12 Deficiency &amp; Iron-Deficiency Anemia<\/li><li>Medication Absorption Changes:<ul><li>Increased Absorption:<ul><li>Digoxin<\/li><li><strong>Lithium<\/strong><\/li><li>Penicillin<\/li><li>Atorvastatin<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Decreased Absorption:<ul><li>Phenytoin<\/li><li>Erythromycin<\/li><li>Coumadin<\/li><li>Ampicillin<\/li><li>Tamoxifen<\/li><li>Cyclosporine<\/li><li>Levonorgestrel<\/li><li>Imatinib<\/li><li>Tacrolimus<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-a9d9a21\" data-id=\"a9d9a21\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e9b87b3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e9b87b3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-10684 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Gastric-Bypass.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"801\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Gastric-Bypass.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Gastric-Bypass-187x300.jpg 187w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>RYGB <sup>1<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e473fc1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e473fc1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-10691 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/RYGB-Mesenteric-Defects.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"481\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/RYGB-Mesenteric-Defects.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/RYGB-Mesenteric-Defects-300x289.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Mesenteric Defects; (a) Petersen&#8217;s Space, (b) Transverse Mesocolon Defect, (c) Jejuno-Jejunostomy Defect <sup>3<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-0289c24 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"0289c24\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-5453252\" data-id=\"5453252\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8d3955f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8d3955f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Jejunoileal Bypass<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-78c43ed elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"78c43ed\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-ae06b81\" data-id=\"ae06b81\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-40a51b2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"40a51b2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Procedure<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Divide Proximal Jejunum at 35 cm<\/li><li>Anastomose to Proximal End to Ileum, 10 cm From Ileocecal Valve<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Basics<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>No Longer Preformed<\/li><li>High Complication Rate \u2013 Liver Cirrhosis, Kidney Stones, Osteopenia &amp; Malnutrition<ul><li>Reoperate if Found<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-f524923\" data-id=\"f524923\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dace48d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dace48d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-10681 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Jejunoileal-Bypass.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"256\" height=\"416\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Jejunoileal-Bypass.jpg 256w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Jejunoileal-Bypass-185x300.jpg 185w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px\" \/><\/p><p>Jejunoileal Bypass <sup>4<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-d89c8bd elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"d89c8bd\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-9c11508\" data-id=\"9c11508\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b24ced9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b24ced9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Biliopancreatic Diversion with Duodenal Switch (BPD-DS)<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-abc1669 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"abc1669\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-62da5cd\" data-id=\"62da5cd\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-520b013 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"520b013\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Procedure<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Preform a Sleeve Gastrectomy<\/li><li>Divide Ileum 250 cm From Ileocecal Valve<\/li><li>Anastomose Proximal End (Ileoileostomy) 100 cm from Ileocecal Valve<\/li><li>Divide Duodenum 3-4 cm Distal to Pylorus<\/li><li>Anastomose Roux Limb to Duodenum (Duodenoileostomy)<\/li><li>Close Mesenteric Defect<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Considerations<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>May Require Two-Stage Procedure if Extremely High BMI &gt; 70<ul><li>Stage 1: Sleeve Gastrectomy<\/li><li>Stage 2: Diversion &amp; Switch After 1 Year of Weight Loss<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Duodenal Switch Leaves the Pylorus Intact<ul><li>Biliopancreatic Diversion Alone Has Roux Limb Anastomose to Stomach<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-64a25ca\" data-id=\"64a25ca\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-918fff4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"918fff4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-10683 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Biliopanncreatic-Diversion.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"809\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Biliopanncreatic-Diversion.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Biliopanncreatic-Diversion-185x300.jpg 185w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>BPD-DS <sup>1<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-8d2be80 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"8d2be80\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-2ee101c\" data-id=\"2ee101c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<d